text: In the office, where work is done With deadlines and tasks to be won There's one person who sets the tone Who makes everyone feel at home The boss with a smile on their face Brings joy and happiness to all in place They lead by example, they inspire And make sure that everyone gets higher They encourage growth and development And celebrate each team member's achievement They listen to feedback and suggestions And always strive for improvement and progression So if you want to find a happy workplace Where people are motivated and awake Just look for a boss like this one Who brings positivity and fun
